Package org.opt4j.core.config

Class Icons

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.opt4j.core.config.Icons
  • public class Icons
extends Object
    The Icons class is used to get ImageIcons from a given filename. Moreover, it contains the filenames of some standard icons.
